<h1>Shipping &amp; Returns</h1>
<div id="contentpage">
			
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;">Shipping</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 18.4px;"><br />
				</span></span></strong><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; background-color: white;">UPS Ground is currently
our only shipping method offered. UPS can only deliver to a street address. NO
PO BOXES. Orders are shipped within two (2) business days from the time the
order is placed. Arrival times vary according to destination.</span></p>
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal">

</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you order
several cases, they may not arrive in the same shipping box. If you receive a box
and it does not contain everything you ordered, check the shipping label for
number of boxes. The remaining cases may be arriving separately.<br />
		
<br />
		
Because we value your feedback, we hope to offer other shipping methods in the
future.
		<o:p></o:p></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"></span></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><strong>Shipping Charge</strong></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 10pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Shipping charges are
automatically calculated and set by UPS using the total weight of product in
your order and shipping address. You will always have an opportunity to see the
full amount of your purchase with the shipping charge before you confirm your order.</span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><strong>Canadian Shipping</strong></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Massimo Zanetti Beverage USA has contracted with <span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">UPS</span> for all shipments to its customers in Canada. All orders will be sent using <span style="FONT-WEIGHT: bold">UPS Standard</span> to/from Canada. <br />
		
			
			
			
			
			<br />
		
			
			
			
			
			<span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">UPS can only deliver to a street address. NO PO BOXES. Shipping charges will be paid through this on-line store. You will always have an opportunity to see the full amount of your purchase including the shipping charge before you confirm your order. <br />
			
				
				
				
				
				</span><br />
		
			
			
			
			
			Canada Customs requires Canadian recipients to pay applicable duties and taxes on each shipment entering Canada. These charges may include PST, GST, HST, duties and other taxes of goods (e.g. excise tax). A brokerage fee may also be charged to process shipments and present the requisite customs paperwork to Canada Customs on the importer's behalf. <br />
		
			
			
			
			
			<br />
		
			
			
			
			
			Your order will be shipped under UPS's e-Tailer Brokerage Program (eBP), where eligible shipments imported into Canada for non-commercial purposes and valued under CAD$ 200 shipped via UPS Standard service are subject to a reduced brokerage fee of CAD$ 10, plus any applicable duties and taxes. Shipments valued at CAD$ 200 and above and/or being imported to Canada for commercial purposes and/or subject to specialized clearance may incur additional fees. <br />
		
			
			
			
			
			<br />
		
			
			
			
			
			Please, be aware that UPS will request payment of these charges at the time of delivery. You have the ability to call UPS ahead of time (1-800-742-5877) to pay these charges, eliminating the need for payment on delivery.<br />
		
			
			
			
			
			<br />
		
			
			
			
			
			All shipping charges, customs fees, brokerage fees and any other delivery fees associated with delivery of an order are the responsibility of the customer. Customers must agree to these terms prior to finalizing their order. Shipping charges do not include customs fees, brokerage fees or any other associated fees, all of which are the sole responsibility of the customer at time of delivery. The customer is responsible for any return shipping charges, if applicable. 
			
			
			
			
			
		<o:p></o:p></span></p><span style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 115%;"><br />
	
		
		
		
		
		
		
		
		
		
		
	<p style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt" class="MsoNormal"><strong>UPS Guarantees and Notices 
				
				
				
				
				
			<o:p></o:p></strong></p></span>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Subject to the Tariff/Terms and Conditions of Service, UPS guarantees on-schedule delivery of packages shipped via UPS's services listed as guaranteed, or will refund your transportation charges. Guaranteed Service is not available in all locations and scheduled business days and delivery schedules are revised occasionally due to changes in distribution and volume. Service to some remote areas also may require additional delivery days. For current delivery schedules, service availability and information, and a description of the UPS Service Guarantee, see the UPS Rate and Service Guide. Certain commodities and high value shipments may require additional transit time for customs clearance. 
			
			
			
			
			
		<o:p></o:p></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Please Note: Shipping rates are based on the information you have supplied. Shipping rates do not include duties, taxes, or other non-routine customs brokerage charges. Other shipping charges, surcharges, or accessorial charges also may apply. Rates are based on UPS published rates. Please see the UPS Rate and Service Guide or the applicable service and rate guide in your jurisdiction for details. 
			
			
			
			
			
		<o:p></o:p></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><strong>International Shipping 
				
				
				
				
				
			<o:p></o:p></strong></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Currently we only ship to Canada and APO/FPO addresses. Due to the cost to ship outside North America; we are not able to ship to other countries at this time. If you live in a country outside the US and Canada, you might like to try </span><a href="http://www.myamericanshopper.com "><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; COLOR: #175d7f; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">www.myamericanshopper.com</span></a><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"> to see if they can assist you with purchasing and shipping our product. <span style="font-style: italic;">Please note that when you enter a link outside of our web store, Massimo Zanetti Beverage USA bears no liability for the contents thereof. 
				
				
				
				
				
			<o:p></o:p></span></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 0pt;" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">APO/FPO</span>
			
			
			
			
			
		<o:p></o:p></strong></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">In support of our troops, we will ship to APO/FPO boxes. Please follow the directions listed below or feel free to contact us at 888-246-2598. 
			
			
			
			
			
		<o:p></o:p></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<p style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt; margin: 0in 0in 10pt;" class="MsoNormal"><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Directions to ship product to APO/FPO boxes: 
			
			
			
			
			
		<o:p></o:p></span></p>
	
	
	
	
	
<ul dir="ltr" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 10pt;">
		
		
		
		
		
	<li><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">Create an account, making sure that the "Customer Information" is the same address used for your credit card billing statement. 
				
				
				
				
				
			<o:p></o:p></span>
			
			
			
			
			
		<div>&nbsp;</div></li>
		
		
		
		
		
	<li><span style="LINE-HEIGHT: 115%; FONT-SIZE: 10pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">When prompted for the "Ship to address," enter 1200 Court Street, Portsmouth, VA 23704. This address is our warehouse and will inform the shipping clerk the order needs to be brought to the front office for shipping. 
				
				
				
				
				
			<o:p></o:p></span>
			
			
			
			
			
		<div>&nbsp;</div></li>
		
		
		
		
		
